</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="165" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="2.[1346,2554,1150,2167]" pageId="2" pageNumber="165">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1346,1584,1662,1695]" pageId="2" pageNumber="165">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but the 
<taxonomicName authority="Woolly Lemur" authorityName="Woolly Lemur" box="[1349,1666,1701,1734]" class="Mammalia" family="Indriidae" genus="Avahi" kingdom="Animalia" order="Primates" pageId="2" pageNumber="165" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="betsileo">Betsileo Woolly Lemur</taxonomicName>
is nocturnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
